{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"C\n    \n      Command Center + Deep Dives\n      A single AI-powered command center as the home screen — population health overview with live KPIs, AI-surfaced alerts, and intervention recommendations. Every other screen (Cohortisation, Builder, Patients, Comms, Outcomes) is a deep-dive accessible from the command center's cards and alerts.\n      \n        Pros\n          Opens with impact — \"here's your population, here's what needs attention NOW\"\n          AI is front-and-center from the first screen, not buried in a tab\n          Natural drill-down: alert → patient → action → outcome\n          Demo story writes itself: \"You log in. AI tells you 12 patients need attention. Click one. See the summary. Send the outreach. Done.\"\n        \n        Cons\n          Command center is the most complex single screen to build\n          Builder and Cohortisation config feel less prominent (accessed via settings/config area)\n        \n      \n      Best for: When you want AI to be the headline capability and the app to feel like an intelligent system, not a dashboard","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1775495087348}
